{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"586f726c4a","title":"江青讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1ff847fc2a","index":0,"year":1966,"month":10,"day":6,"articleId":"586f726c4a"}],"tags":[{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","name":"无产阶级文化大革命参考资料（1966年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8408247a11","type":"paragraph","text":"在全国在京革命师生向资产阶级","index":0,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"283ccc07dc","type":"paragraph","text":"反动路线猛烈开火普师大会上","index":1,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"3f8cdc94d7","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志的酷","index":2,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"b158b09e8e","type":"paragraph","text":"（10月6日）同志们、同学们","index":3,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"81f7537ab5","type":"paragraph","text":"你们好！我受觉中央和毛主席的委托间你们好：中央文化革命全体同志周你们好！向你们致崇高的无产阶极革命的敬礼！","index":4,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"2f0289ea66","type":"paragraph","text":"我们支持你何这种大无畏的无产阶极的英雄行为，我们学习你们不怕困难，不怕性的革命精神！我们坚决和你们站在一起，掉卫党中央十一中全会关于无产阶级文化大革命的决定，即十六条","index":5,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"669d82241c","type":"paragraph","text":"一个真正的无产阶极革命者一定要掌握原则，掌握政策。希望同志们在大风大浪的炼中掌握稳政策，学会善于运用斗争的策略，最重要的是在展列主义毛泽东思想原则基础上，在斗争的考过程中，发展壮大左派队伍，团粘大多数愿意革命的人，团粘那些受蒙的人，孤立和打击一小摄党内走套本主义道路的当权派。","index":6,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"d8060eed7a","type":"paragraph","text":"党中央在十月五日批准了军队关于无产阶极文化大革命的紧急通知，现在请张春桥同志向同志们宣好不好？（答：好！）","index":7,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"88eed91872","type":"paragraph","text":"北京机械学院《16102》战斗队","index":8,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"4562310a57","type":"paragraph","text":"糖印十月九日首都红卫兵报北京汽车分公司文革大学报办公室","index":9,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"01b2f77bd7","type":"paragraph","text":"1966年10月25日","index":10,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"610226a3bc","type":"paragraph","text":"十月六日工人体育场","index":11,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"1ed548b8ba","type":"paragraph","text":"大会上与中央首长谈话康生：（看了我们“两条路斗争”后）","index":12,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"83fa12a311","type":"paragraph","text":"你何这个“两条路的斗争”写得很好：你们批制赵如章批判得好幅：我们中央文革小粗的都支持你偶。","index":13,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"a52bde39bf","type":"paragraph","text":"（我们请康生同志给我们文章做批示康生：我很好地在看一逼。翻富治：力夫的斋就是修正主义的，你们在国防科委斗争二十八天、做得对、干得好！我早就支持少","index":14,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"14c456cabe","type":"paragraph","text":"数派的斗争！","index":15,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"248bb5bde9","type":"paragraph","text":"（我们：我们在斗争观苦的时候要防右，而在斗争顺利的时候要防“左”，注意政策和策略）翻富治：有水平，并指示要注意争取大多数。","index":16,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"363ab50d90","type":"paragraph","text":"（我们宣传毛泽东思想就是要大喊大叫）谢富治：好！","index":17,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"598f7e2e9d","type":"paragraph","text":"（我们我们正在批判力夫站）褐成武：批得好，应胺批","index":18,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"},{"id":"3d1791e7d1","type":"paragraph","text":"·235。","index":19,"publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a"}],"page":{"id":"70ae581699","publicationId":"cb043827-1a6a-46f3-863d-a430958e5a0d","articleId":"586f726c4a","start":245,"end":245}}}},"__N_SSG":true}